metadata.title: Aquatop Replacement Carbon Cartridge 2-Pack for All Venti Desktop Aquariums, VDA-02-RC
features: The Aquatop Venti Replacement 2-pack is the only cartridge specifically designed for the Venti Professional Showcase Aquarium. This combination of small porosity polymer floss and premium carbon will maintain the ideal aquatic environment with a fresh cartridge every month. Each package is a 2 month supply.
